extends layout

block head
  script(src='https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js' async='' defer='')

block content
  section.pb-2.mt-2.mb-4
    img(src='/menehune-full.png' width='200px' height='200px' alt='menehune' class='img-fluid')
    h3.border-bottom How to use Menehune URL
    p Please sign in or create an account to access URL shortening services.
    p Once signed in, click the Shortener category in the navigation bar. Further instruction will be on the shortener page.


  section.pb-2.mt-2.mb-4
    h5.border-bottom About
    p Menehune URL Shortener
    p External URL shorteners have been used with malicious intent and have been blocked from within the state network.
    p Menehune URL Shortener helps solve this by increasing authenticity and non-repudiation of URLs through the use of user accounts and threat detection.

  section.pb-2.mt-2.mb-4
    h3.border-bottom Mission
    p Shorten all of the links

  section.pb-2.mt-2.mb-4
  h3.border-bottom What makes this different
  .container.text-center
    .row.align-items-start
      section.col
        img(src='/opensourced.jpg' alt='' width='150' height='150')
        h5 Open-sourced
        p This link management platform was developed with the amdin and users in mind.
      section.col
        img(src='/reliable.jpg' alt='' width='150' height='150')
        h5 Reliable
        p A major issue faced when using other shorteners is the shortened urls containing malware. This platform compares known malicious factors and alerts you when these factors are detected.
      section.col
        img(src='/culture.jpg' alt='' width='150' height='150')
        h5 Culture
